docker run -d --name mynginx -p 8080:80 nginx

Your Browser
      │
http://localhost:8080
      │
      ▼
Windows Port 8080
      │
      ▼
Docker Engine
      │
      ▼
Container Port 80
      │
      ▼
Nginx Web Server


http://localhost:8080

the request goes to:

Windows (or WSL)
Docker Engine
Docker forwards it to port 80 inside the container.
Nginx receives the request and sends back the web page.



